<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Discord Friends==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Seen in the Social tab under "All Friends", this feature allows you to see your Discord friends with their current status and to perform different actions. Friends with a Discord account linked will have a Discord icon displayed on their profile
</div> 

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
If your friend has linked their Discord account to their VRChat account, you will be able to invite them to join your instance through Discord. Otherwise, you will be able to invite them to create a VRChat account. You or your friends may prevent your VRChat account from being shown in the Discord section by turning off the "Allow Discord Friends" setting in the '''Comfort & Safety''' section of the settings.
</div>

